Message: * A friend wanted you to see this item from WRAL.com: http://wral.com/13710929

— Fifteen-year-old Laezia Avion Faison, known as "Peachezz," was found safe today in Warsaw, according to the Garner Police Department.

Warsaw is located about an hour southeast of Garner.

A tweet sent by the Garner Police Department said Faison is in good health and is being returned to her parents. Investigators said Faison has family in Warsaw.

Garner police asked for the public's help yesterday to find the teen. She had not been seen since around noon on May 28 at Garner Magnet High School and had last contacted her friends on Monday, according to investigators.
